{
  "stem": "7904.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Like I mentioned before, that was a cultural home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We all read.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We had newspapers home, books, and--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish and Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sisters, between themself, they spoke Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they also knew Jewish very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We spoke Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father-- we were a shomer Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like before the war, like, you know, 50, 60 years ago, there was no such a thing like not to be a shomer Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he was-- he was more pragmatic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He understood that if the business-- first of all, he has to attend the business world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Otherwise there's not going to be no [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was a very-- he was a very wise man, smart man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was very good in business, trustworthy, like I said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All of us worked-- later on, worked in the business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because we had to see the customers to go to collect the money, because all the business was on credit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And twice a month-- twice a month was payday in Poland, the 15th and the 1st of the month.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we had to-- we had bicycles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, there was no such a thing, like here in the United States, you have a car, you have a truck.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "No, we had bicycles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I traveled-- we traveled-- I traveled by bicycle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We employed about 10 people, mostly-- mostly with the horse and you know-- horse and how you call it?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Horse and buggy, yeah?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So most of-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And like I said, we were very well off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody knew my name-- our name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The sister.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I met here a person a couple years ago, and I ask her-- she ask me, what is my name.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she asked me, did you have a sister [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Topcha? ?] I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
